{"tid":973832,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過晌街見到個陌生人然後個人會有啲奇怪嘅感覺","createTime":"2019-01-08T12:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T16:13:37.000Z","uid":138812,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7ed373b371e99b747e1ff9ac98e6e43c5e2809","tid":973832,"uid":138812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我今日晌地鐵度見到個路人，不過無留意佢，但係我後尾走左之後好想再見翻佢望下佢，行翻轉頭佢已經去到好遠，之後我就好頹好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後尾翻到屋企仲喊到癡左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但明明我係唔識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比一個陌生人牽動情緒嘅感覺好奇怪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無巴打有類似嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過其實我都覺得成件事有少少唔合理 我自己都唔係幾接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce15dc90dbf3df5934457a2194f63bd7094db3af","tid":973832,"uid":142532,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:35:17.000Z","msg":"有無諗過嗰個唔係人?"},{"pid":"ea3a9c3323a70ea9c2e8a496b403c2ad0619a69c","tid":973832,"uid":66099,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"食藥未？"},{"pid":"a02b5a0e5553e7cd1b40ae217c2590a12d8c6f13","tid":973832,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:36:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"634233ebfb70253f8cd224a74924c6641d8bd264","tid":973832,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"有...<br />\n個一晚佢無擺低錢就走咗去！係街度撞到佢真係眼濕濕"},{"pid":"b67dc041d69417085c21e053075da12ec40c4cb9","tid":973832,"uid":138812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea3a9c3323a70ea9c2e8a496b403c2ad0619a69c","tid":973832,"uid":66099,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"食藥未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"認真po <img